headline: United Rentals (URI): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q4 Earnings?
summary: Over the last six months, United Rentals’s shares have sunk to $629.21, producing a disappointing 19.7% loss while the S&P 500 was flat. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
